로 6개월간 활동하게 됩니다.   한달에 2병씩 피이니스트 와인을 소개해 드리겠습니다.   제가 와인에 대한 지식이 없으므로 제 소개 포스팅은   지극히 일반인의 눈높이에서 시작될것입니다.   차차 시간이 지나면 좀더 나아지겠죠 ㅎㅎ   이번달에 소개해드릴 2병의 와인은 과연 어디서 먹을까?   벌써부터 고민입니다 ㅎㅎㅎ   그럼 다음 소개 포스팅에서 만나요^^.  ","images":["http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_80/esc1212_1416329137048KdQrU_JPEG/1.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_7/esc1212_1416329470344oip0I_JPEG/9.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141119_262/esc1212_14163295663100aYoX_JPEG/IMG_4763.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_60/esc1212_1416329797565XI9yT_JPEG/4.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_293/esc1212_141632979783853Ay6_JPEG/6.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_85/esc1212_1416330073849SfYEN_JPEG/7.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_204/esc1212_1416330104740RA8Ez_JPEG/8.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_61/esc1212_1416330328733ODkgp_JPEG/32.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_15/esc1212_1416330471856rr5k9_JPEG/10.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_153/esc1212_1416330580157dbyr9_JPEG/11-tile.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141119_102/esc1212_1416330611690MtCCH_JPEG/15.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_20/esc1212_1416331256006DEUws_GIF/20141115181818.gif?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_185/esc1212_1416331290217uhFOb_GIF/20141115182245.gif?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_100/esc1212_1416333234363wviIS_JPEG/17.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_153/esc1212_1416331389957mt9wW_JPEG/19.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141119_238/esc1212_1416331390187gtmY8_JPEG/20.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_63/esc1212_1416331617437zGOee_JPEG/18.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141119_98/esc1212_1416331617749MnzoV_JPEG/21.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_296/esc121